n]], Knight, ''6 May 1884''<ref name=\"p81\"/>\n** [[Gold Medal of Military Valour]], ''4 September 1916''<ref name=\"Decorato\">[http://www.quirinale.it/onorificenze/insigniti/12519 \"Romanov Nicola II Czar di Russia\"] (in Italian), ''Il sito ufficiale della Presidenza della Repubblica''. Retrieved 5 August 2018.</ref>\n* [[File:Flag of the Vatican City (2 by 3).svg|25px]] [[Holy See]]: [[Order of the Holy Sepulchre]], Grand Cross, ''6 May 1884''\n* {{flagicon|Sovereign Military Order of Malta}} [[Military Order of Malta]]: Bailiff Grand Cross of Honour and Devotion<ref name=\"p81\"/>\n* {{Flag|Empire of Japan}}: [[Order of the Rising Sun]], Grand Cordon with Paulownia Flowers, ''4 September 1882''\n* {{flagicon image|Flag of Bogd Khaanate Mongolia.svg}} [[Bogd Khanate of Mongolia|Mongolia]]: Order of the Precious Rod, ''1913''\n* {{Flag|Principality of Montenegro}}: [[Order of Prince Danilo I]], Grand Cross<ref>[http://www.orderofdanilo.org/en/news/051207.htm \"The Order of Sovereign Prince Danilo I\"], ''orderofdanilo.org''. {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101009012208/http://www.orderofdanilo.org/en/history/index.htm |data=9 October 2010 }}</ref>\n* {{Flag|Netherlands}}: [[Order of the Netherlands Lion]], Grand Cross, ''15 March 1881''\n* {{Flag|Ottoman Empire}}: [[Order of Osmanieh]], 1st Class, ''28 July 1884''\n* {{flagicon image|Amir Kabir Flag.svg}} [[Qajar Iran|Persian Empire]]: Order of the August Portrait, ''28 July 1884''\n* {{Flag|Kingdom of Portugal|1830}}: [[Sash of the Two Orders]] ([[Order of Christ (Portugal)|Christ]] and [[Order of Aviz|Aviz]]), Grand Cross, ''25 May 1881''; [[Sash of the Three Orders|Three Orders]], ''9 April 1896''<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Bragan\u00e7a |first1=Jose Vicente de|last2=Estrela |first2=Paulo Jorge |date=2017 |title=Troca de Decora\u00e7\u00f5es entre os Reis de Portugal e os Imperadores da R\u00fassia|url=https://www.academia.edu/35782766/TROCA_DE_CONDECORA%C3%87%C3%95ES_ENTRE_OS_REIS_DE_PORTUGAL_E_